<p>I want to slide my layout from top to bottom and remain visible. below is the code which do layout from bottom to top.</p>  <pre><code>&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?&gt; &lt;translate xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:duration="400" android:fillAfter="true" android:fromYDelta="100%p" android:interpolator="@android:anim/bounce_interpolator" android:toYDelta="0%p" /&gt; </code></pre>